<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Components: &lt;segment field name (ST)&gt; ^ &lt;value1 (ST) &amp; value2 (ST) &amp; value3 (ST&#8230;&#8203;&gt;</p></td>
